JOHANNESBURG – Ashwin Willemse's biographer on Monday weighed in on the former Springbok winger's studio walkout. Heindrich Wyngaard said the relationship between Willemse and SuperSport rugby analyst Nick Mallet appears to have been strained for some time and the incident was bound to happen. Wyngaard said regular rugby viewers will have noticed there was no love lost between Mallet and Willemse. WATCH: No word from SuperSport about #AshwinWillemse Willemse slammed fellow presenters Naas Botha and Mallet on air saying he will not be patronised by two individuals who played during the apartheid era. SuperSport said it is investigating the incident. eNCA